title: The One Where Lala Visits 50 Cent on Set
description:
Pop the Perrier and get ready for details about Lala and 50 Cent’s reunion and how that went down along with a little tea from #PumpRules filming! Lala & Jess also discuss Teresa Giudice’s wedding and $10k hairdo, Lala’s first sexy time post-break up, BravoCon, Give Them Lala Beauty, and the color currently giving Lala “all the vibes!”
